Example charts

Source: vignettes/Examples copy.Rmd
Examples copy.Rmd
chart <- GC_chart(
  ophA_clusters, 
  cluster = "cluster", 
  group = "class", 
  height = "250px") %>%
  GC_legend(FALSE)
# Generate links
links <- get_links(
            chart, group = "name", 
            value1 = c("ophB1", "ophC"), 
            value2 = c("dbophB1", "dbophC"),
            cluster = c(1,2)
            )

# Add links to chart
chart %>% GC_links(links)
# Generate links
links <- get_links(
            chart, group = "name", 
            value1 = c("ophB1", "ophC"), 
            value2 = c("dbophB1", "dbophC"),
            cluster = c(1,2)
            )

# Add links to chart
chart %>% GC_links(links)
# Generate links
links <- get_links(
            chart, group = "name", 
            value1 = c("ophB1", "ophC"), 
            value2 = c("dbophB1", "dbophC"),
            cluster = c(1,2)
            )

# Add links to chart
chart %>% GC_links(links) %>% GC_labels("name")
